{"tid":1247993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［白杖係攻擊武器］寄左信去平機會有回覆","createTime":"2019-06-21T10:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T16:10:06.000Z","uid":107178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"52bf18fafcb8485f2d35c8292f3cf9ce0b0af536","tid":1247993,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:10:21.000Z","msg":"之前寫左封信去平機會投訴啲警犬當白杖係攻擊性武器，平機會話受害人無去投訴，所以做唔到野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1H0C4P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1H0C4P.png&h=cba0185a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">In the absence of a substantive case lodged by the aggrieved person, the Commission regrets that we are not in a position to offer any specific comment on the matter you raised. <br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然平機會唔係咩好野，但寄左咁多間暫時得佢地有回覆<br />\n可唔可以推到事件本人去平機會投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e85e500d696822936db44acdf929b068d48fae","tid":1247993,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:09:48.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c705af2fd9afccbf0e6d6057243bc7bd7646dc0f","tid":1247993,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}